OL,3,CMan charged with assisting foreign
OL,4,Cintelligence service relating to Iran
OL,6,FA man has been charged with assisting
OL,7,Fa foreign intelligence service
OL,8,Frelating to Iran after an
OL,9,Finvestigation by Counter Terrorism
OL,10,FPolicing.
OL,12,FVahid Aberi, 39, from Liverpool, was
OL,13,Fcharged with the National Security Act
OL,14,Foffence on Wednesday, 15 July, in
OL,15,FBirmingham.
OL,17,FThe Metropolitan Police said he would
OL,18,Fappear at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,19,FCourt on Friday, 17 July, after
OL,20,Faddresses in Birmingham and Liverpool
OL,21,Fwere searched.
