OL,3,CMan charged with assisting foreign
OL,4,Cintelligence service relating to Iran
OL,6,FAberi's arrest comes after a
OL,7,F"proactive investigation" by Counter
OL,8,FTerrorism Policing.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,16,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,17,Fsaid: "We have seen a significant and
OL,18,Fsustained increase in the tempo of our
OL,19,Fwork in national security
OL,20,Finvestigations in recent years.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@YO]yD@GOU
