PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784395091
OL,3,CMan charged with assisting foreign
OL,4,Cintelligence service relating to Iran
OL,6,F"This case is yet another example of
OL,7,Fwhere we've intervened to disrupt
OL,8,Fsuspected activity linked to foreign
OL,9,Fintelligence services.
OL,11,F"While we can't comment in detail
OL,12,Faround the allegations now that a man
OL,13,Fhas been charged, I do want to
OL,14,Freassure the public that we have not
OL,15,Fidentified any direct threat to them
OL,16,Fnor any threat towards a community or
OL,17,Findividual in connection with this
OL,18,Finvestigation."
OL,20,FAberi was remanded in custody.
